descriptionHtml:
There are a lot of useless rubbish in Skyrim, I was wondering what to do with it? So, I decide to put them into cookpot and then...eat it. Our character can eat dragon souls, so why he couldn't eat a broom for example? Or any ingot? Or troll skull? Such a diet for noble hero.
Â Now, if you as me have endless loot in your pockets, just find cookpot and make something tasty.

ps. if you use mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30726/?]Dine with followers[/url], your food will appear in the plate, like on my screens.
author: CobaltReptile
